en.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aDemographyxGermany. 0aHousing forecastingxGermany. 0aPopulation forecastingxGermany. 0aReal propertyxGermany. 4aAlterung. 4aBüroimmobilien. 4aEinzelhandelsimmobilien. 4aInvestoren. 4aPflegeimmobilien. 4aStadtentwickler. 4aZuwanderung. 7aBUSINESS & ECONOMICS / Management.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Business and Economics 2000 - 2014z9783110635737oZDB-23-GBE08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruyterteBook-Paket OWV/AV  BWL, VWL 2013z9783110342659oZDB-23-OAV0 cprintz978348671364040uhttps://doi.org/10.1524/978348671915440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783486719154423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783486719154/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LAEC  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-GBEc2000d2014  aZDB-23-OAVb2013